<p>
<note n="0421008" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0421008">串＝慣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0422003" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0422003">非＝悲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0423002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0423002">根＝相【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0425001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0425001">故彼＝彼故【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0425002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0425002">〔為〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
